dct_title_s: Map of the Colony of Natal to accompany the paper by Dr. R. J. Mann
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. County divisions within colony are shown. Surrounding territories of Zulu Land, Orange River Free State, Basuto Land, and Adam Kok's Land are labeled. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 37 (1867), pp. 48-67; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.37 1867
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1867.
